  m_text: 'Thank you for taking the time to playtest this game. I am looking for
    feedback on how I can improve the game experience. Thus, I ask that you look
    beyond just the gameplay for feedback. Click the buttons above for some pointers
    on what to look out for.


    The game is still not fully complete. I have not
    finished much of the UI. If you have any ideas for the UI, I would love to hear
    it in the feedback form.'
